                detailedExample: 'The MBB decision — which firm fits YOU?\n\nChoose McKinsey if: You want maximum global brand, love data-driven intellectual debate, are comfortable being challenged constantly, and have an exceptional academic record.\n\nChoose BCG if: Innovation projects excite you, you enjoy open creative thinking, want strong DACH/European exposure, and value a slightly more collaborative environment.\n\nChoose Bain if: Team culture matters deeply to you, you prefer results over elegant presentations, want PE exposure, and value tight alumni loyalty.\n\nHonest truth: Apply to all three. The culture difference only becomes real once you\'re inside. Always research the SPECIFIC OFFICE you\'re applying to — Munich BCG has a different feel from London BCG.',
